#### **Preview Builds (Local Testing)**

Preview builds allow you to test your app on physical devices without going through the App Store or TestFlight:

```bash
# Create a preview build for iOS (installable on physical devices)
npx eas-cli build --platform ios --profile preview

# Create a preview build for Android (installable on physical devices)
npx eas-cli build --platform android --profile preview

# Create preview builds for both platforms
npx eas-cli build --platform all --profile preview
```

#### **Development Builds (With Native Code)**

For testing native modules or custom native code:

```bash
